title: 854 Picnic Time Circo
description:
The Circo swivels open to reveal four stainless steel cheese tools with eco-friendly rubberwood handles. The board has over 82 square inches of cutting surface and features recessed moat along the board's edge to catch cheese brine or juice from cut fruit. The Circo makes a thoughtful gift for any cheese connoisseur!

Components:
1 hard cheese knife
1 cheese shaver
1 fork-tipped cheese knife
1 cheese spreader

transcripts: The Circo by Picnic Time is compact, convenient, and classic. This circular chopping board is made of eco-friendly rubber wood. The board swings open to reveal four stainless steel cheese tools with rubber wood handles. The tools include a cheese cleaver, a cheese plane, a fork cheese knife, and a cheese spreading knife. The Circo has over 182 square inches of cutting surface and features a recessed moat on the board's edge to catch the cheese brine or juice from cut fruit. The Circo makes a thoughtful gift and great party centerpiece.
